arStrings.szText: My son was wiser than even the Horadrim, but it was not in his nature to be a shepherd either.
His Prophecy was a warning, but rather than use it to unite Sanctuary, he let it breed chaos.
Inarius. Elias. Lorath. They wanted so badly to see their own meaning in the Prophecy, they were blind to the simple truth of it.
We are prisoners of the Eternal Conflict. The pawns of angels and demons.
It will always be a part of us. We must fight to survive.
